            <description><![CDATA[【[磕到了]大腿粗的人可能更健康！】很多人会为自己的大腿粗而惆怅，比如裤子总是挑不到合适的，大腿缝中间还容易磨损。请记住，这一定是裤子的问题，你的大腿好着呢！因为大腿粗的人可能更健康<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>但如果你的腰围、颈围比较粗，可就得小心了👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（cctv生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4940371713523737" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hheiyx1hgnj21hc0u0tcn.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/FUMvSWLmlx088cJdCtby01041200CcEw0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1695693321&amp;ssig=JNnBDspdXM&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/OZDnAfFQlx088cJcTcNq01041200j2yK0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1695693321&amp;ssig=Xr16%2FkxV6m&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/7MCK0Kemlx088cJcSuzu01041200bVam0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1695693321&amp;ssig=hBYSAIkq7b&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4940371713523737" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
